releaseNotes:
Version 4.4.2:

• Prioritising search results that match the current AutoFill request’s URL host;
• Fixed rare deadlock when saving an item while sync was in progress;
• Other minor bug fixes and improvements.

Version 4.4.1:

• Fixed a crash that could occur when performing an AutoFill.
• Fixed export of historic passwords using the new credential exchange.

- 
Version 4.4 brings some minor new features and bug fixes:

• Added an option to view the index of each character in a password;
• Added support for the upcoming credential exchange feature on both macOS and iOS;
• Moved crash reporting and analytics from AppCenter, which is shutting down, to Firebase;
• Fixed a few minor leaks;
• Many other minor bug fixes.
